    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts promptly and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides reliable shifting, making it a dependable choice for daily commuting. While the exterior paint remains vibrant, there are a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular road use. The interior is clean and well-preserved, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. All major mechanical systems are functioning as intended, offering a solid driving experience for its next owner.",
