    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super well-maintained, so you can just hop in and go! It runs like a dream and is perfect for anyone looking for a reliable, comfy ride that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve loved owning this beauty, and I know you will too\u2014come by and take it for a test drive!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
