    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new companion for the road? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem that\u2019s been so good to me. It\u2019s in great shape, runs like a dream, and is ready to hit the pavement for many more miles. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is super comfortable and dependable. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 33500.0,
