      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a mechanically sound example featuring a robust, naturally aspirated 3.0L inline-six power plant paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. This vehicle exhibits excellent throttle response and linear power delivery, benefiting from a recently refreshed VANOS system and upgraded polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in. The rear-wheel-drive platform maintains a near 50/50 weight distribution, complemented by an active limited-slip differential and a bespoke coilover setup that enhances lateral grip without compromising street driveability. While the chassis shows minor signs of age consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the compression numbers are strong across all cylinders, and the cooling system has been fully overhauled with an aluminum radiator to prevent heat soak. This is a turnkey performance machine ready for the canyons or the commute.",
